{
  "stem": "15115.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He paid me in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I started doing business, black market again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I started-- all of a sudden already we had-- we're talking about now quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were some babies around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some kids came in from different camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I started-- I opened myself a big-- took a big table in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Feldafing was only Jewish people, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- I went to Germany, in Munich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was buying from the Germans shoe polish, ladies' garters, many-- combs, you know, things that everybody needed, you know, because we didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I put a big table and I was selling in and out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I was selling safes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, like I used to blow shapes out of balloons, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the kind of a business I was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That started pretty good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then in the-- in camp, in Feldafing, I opened myself a little store, a mini store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I made-- I built a store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like a six by six, made of wood, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the first store was built in Feldafing, which was against the law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were not allowed to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I had a Greek behind me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were all my friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were all tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Greeks were very, very tough after liberation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Greeks who survived was the-- not the cream of-- it wasn't the cream of Salonica.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the rough Salonica.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "These people were stevedores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were hard people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Like lawyers and doctors and bookkeepers never survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They died right away in Birkenau or any other camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the people who survived, the pictures you got over there, you know, all the-- they're all-- none of them is a lawyer or a doctor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We're all working guys, poor people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
